race.description: Picklebet Get Your Pickle On Plate
race.comment: MISHANI CROWN (7) showed good early pace over 1200m at Beaudesert last time and kept going to score by 1.1 lengths. Should settle handy in the run from an inside barrier and is well-placed to go back-to-back. KEEPMEINTHELOPE (1) saluted at Beaudesert two runs ago, improving again, and then missed the hat-trick 1.75 lengths over 1200m at Sunshine Coast. Races forward and has an inside barrier and 1.5kg claim. Will get every chance to bounce. CARDIOLOGIST (5) resumes and has switched from a top Victorian barn. He's right up to this at best, and the betting should guide to his readiness. CALL OUT (9) resumes for the Campton yard and also deserves a close market watch.
